SUMMARY:Light in the Valley
DESCRIPTION:Light in the Valley exists to empower sufferers of chronic illness to use their brokenness to build godly character and to see themselves as someone with a greater purpose.\nAdvanced notice of your interest/participation is appreciated. \nAll inquiries will be kept confidential and sent directly to the group leader. \nEmail Contact: lightinthevalley@calvarychurch.org\nInterest Form\nhttps://calvarychurchpa.wufoo.com/forms/qiqzx0q1s9gd7g
URL:https://www.calvarychurch.org/calendar/light-in-the-valley-7/
