SUMMARY:Abiding Hope
DESCRIPTION:Abiding Hope is a support group for Christian parents of a child that has embraced an LGBTQ+ identity. Our purpose is to come alongside parents by sharing the comfort of Jesus Christ and wisdom to navigate the relational waters of loving their child while holding on to the truth of scripture.\nAdvanced notice of your interest/participation is needed. \nAll inquiries will be kept confidential and sent directly to the group leader.\nEmail Contact: abidinghope@calvarychurch.org\nInterest Form\nhttps://calvarychurchpa.wufoo.com/forms/qiqzx0q1s9gd7g
URL:https://www.calvarychurch.org/calendar/abiding-hope-3/
CATEGORIES:Pastoral Care,Website Calendar
END:VEVENT
